{"tid":2340062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警總女文員染疫 本周第二宗","createTime":"2020-12-25T06:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T07:12:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e915e057042463132f52bd3e4a953ecd173cfee3","tid":2340062,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T06:46:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201225/ACVSDDMR5VHOTBBZK5X2DUXH5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201225%2FACVSDDMR5VHOTBBZK5X2DUXH5Y%2F&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=910bfb6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201225%2FACVSDDMR5VHOTBBZK5X2DUXH5Y%2F&h=b2a44194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201225/ACVSDDMR5VHOTBBZK5X2DUXH5Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警總女文員染疫 本周第二宗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/k1yD_mcHOjpTRKOiR4TTnmHxcFc=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AZE3PUDNKFBLNAVZ3237Q2EY3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fk1yD_mcHOjpTRKOiR4TTnmHxcFc%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAZE3PUDNKFBLNAVZ3237Q2EY3A.jpg&h=cc375117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警察總部一周內有兩名女文職人員中招。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】近日警員確診數字急升。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：92患者曾到訪 舞肺重災區  金儷星被控犯聚 違口罩令<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未知兩個案有否關連<br />\n<br />\n今次是一周內第二名於警總工作的女文職人員中招，本月19日亦有一名駐守警總的女文員初步確診，她最後一日上班為本月16日。本月已有至少16名警員確診武肺。<br />\n<br />\n警方指高度關注事件，與該名文職人員可能有緊密接觸的警員及文職人員，均獲安排接受檢疫及病毒檢測；並已即時派員清潔及消毒該名人員的相關工作地方；警方亦經常提醒同事注意個人衞生，減少社交接觸，減低傳染風險，如有任何不適，須立即向處方呈報並求醫。惟警方並無交代上述兩宗發生於警總的確診個案，是否有關連，亦未交代需要隔離檢疫的警員人數。<br />\n<br />\n警隊前日亦一日內有兩宗初步確診個案，兩名23及41歲的軍裝巡邏小隊男警中招，二人分別駐守牛頭角分區及西區分區，早前均有家人確診，懷疑因此受感染。"},{"pid":"0cd7fc6774eac26c24a976f655fa5c5f589bf98e","tid":2340062,"uid":23635,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T06:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hfhO9TW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhfhO9TW.gif&h=a2ab1584&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"511963c46479b682652b04e1fc66bb9e0c982bc3","tid":2340062,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T06:54:44.000Z","msg":"3 萬，thx <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64af96ce17e942a0b06b171b77af6e6ac42d764","tid":2340062,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T06:55:48.000Z","msg":"肉便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33714605fcc755e9b0ec725a44ef2728342af450","tid":2340062,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T06:59:08.000Z","msg":"文員病"},{"pid":"caf407a592e510ec44956f9c9c71aecec862e335","tid":2340062,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T07:12:37.000Z","msg":"警務處女文員？"}]}